Choices, Calculations, OR Slider Labels:
SELECT record, CONCAT_WS(' ', record, if(T2.group_name IS NULL, '?', T2.group_name), pt_initials, date_screen, [user-dag-name]) AS ListVal
FROM (SELECT si.project_id, si.record, si.value AS pt_initials, 
		dt.value AS date_screen, co.value AS gained_consent, gi.value AS group_id
	FROM [data-table] si
		LEFT JOIN [data-table] dt 
			ON (si.project_id = dt.project_id AND si.record = dt.record AND dt.field_name = 'date_screen')
		LEFT JOIN [data-table] co 
			ON (si.project_id = co.project_id AND si.record = co.record AND co.field_name = 'gained_consent')
		LEFT JOIN [data-table] gi 
			ON (si.project_id = gi.project_id AND si.record = gi.record AND gi.field_name = '__GROUPID__')
	WHERE si.project_id=3092 AND si.field_name = 'pt_initials' AND co.value = '1') AS T1
    LEFT JOIN redcap_data_access_groups AS T2 
		ON T1.project_id = T2.project_id AND T1.group_id = T2.group_id
WHERE ((T2.group_name = [user-dag-label] OR T2.group_name = '' OR T2.group_name IS NULL) AND
        record NOT IN
        	(SELECT distinct value FROM [data-table] 
            WHERE project_id=[project-id] AND field_name = 'screening_id' AND record <> [record-name]))
        
        OR record IN 
            (SELECT value FROM [data-table] WHERE project_id=[project-id] AND field_name = 'screening_id' AND record = [record-name])
